𝘚𝘢 𝘪𝘭𝘢𝘭𝘪𝘮 𝘯𝘨 𝘬𝘢𝘮𝘢𝘺 𝘯𝘢 𝘣𝘢𝘬𝘢𝘭, 𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰-𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰𝘯𝘨 𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘪𝘨 𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘱𝘪𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘢𝘩𝘪𝘮𝘪𝘬—𝘩𝘶𝘸𝘢𝘨 𝘯𝘢 𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘩𝘢𝘺𝘢𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘮𝘢𝘶𝘭𝘪𝘵 𝘱𝘢. 

Inaanyayahan ng IAS Student Council ang lahat na makilahok sa "Sa Ilalim ng Kamay na Bakal: Paggunita sa Batas Militar", isang serye ng mga aktibidad na magpapaalala ng katotohanan at magpapatibay ng ating paninindigan: 𝗡𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗿 𝗮𝗴𝗮𝗶𝗻.

Abangan ngayong Setyembre!

Mag-signup para sa Political Forum dito:
https://events.teams.microsoft.com/event/a32365dc-c1d0-4c79-8ffb-17d5ec41ada3@80a45edc-d5ee-46e0-9d75-37c47be9b7cc

Kasama ang FEU Communication Society.

#NeverAgainNeverForget
#FightHistoricalDistortion
#TamarawsRemember

Uunahin. Nalalapitan. Aasikasuhin.
#SerbisyongFirstKa #IASSC79

𝘚𝘢 𝘪𝘭𝘢𝘭𝘪𝘮 𝘯𝘨 𝘬𝘢𝘮𝘢𝘺 𝘯𝘢 𝘣𝘢𝘬𝘢𝘭, 𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰-𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰𝘯𝘨 𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘪𝘨 𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘱𝘪𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘢𝘩𝘪𝘮𝘪𝘬—𝘩𝘶𝘸𝘢𝘨 𝘯𝘢 𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘩𝘢𝘺𝘢𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘮𝘢𝘶𝘭𝘪𝘵 𝘱𝘢.

message.text:
𝘚𝘢 𝘪𝘭𝘢𝘭𝘪𝘮 𝘯𝘨 𝘬𝘢𝘮𝘢𝘺 𝘯𝘢 𝘣𝘢𝘬𝘢𝘭, 𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰-𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰𝘯𝘨 𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘪𝘨 𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘱𝘪𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘢𝘩𝘪𝘮𝘪𝘬—𝘩𝘶𝘸𝘢𝘨 𝘯𝘢 𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘩𝘢𝘺𝘢𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘮𝘢𝘶𝘭𝘪𝘵 𝘱𝘢. 

Inaanyayahan ng IAS Student Council ang lahat na makilahok sa "Sa Ilalim ng Kamay na Bakal: Paggunita sa Batas Militar", isang serye ng mga aktibidad na magpapaalala ng katotohanan at magpapatibay ng ating paninindigan: 𝗡𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗿 𝗮𝗴𝗮𝗶𝗻.

Abangan ngayong Setyembre!

Mag-signup para sa Political Forum dito:
https://events.teams.microsoft.com/event/a32365dc-c1d0-4c79-8ffb-17d5ec41ada3@80a45edc-d5ee-46e0-9d75-37c47be9b7cc

Kasama ang FEU Communication Society.

#NeverAgainNeverForget
#FightHistoricalDistortion
#TamarawsRemember

Uunahin. Nalalapitan. Aasikasuhin.
#SerbisyongFirstKa #IASSC79

message.text:
The campus will be The UAAP's home for tomorrow's Opening Ceremonies. We are excited to welcome our Thomasians and delegates from our partner universities.

Be guided on the campus access points and the arrangement of the participants in the Open Field.

message.text:
CONGRATULATIONS, AUDITIONEES! 🎉👏

After the successful auditions, we now proudly introduce our new batch of trainees! You’ve officially made it in the DCOY family!

You have showcased both talent and determination in braving the auditions. Once again, congratulations to all of you! We look forward to witnessing your growth and sharing the memorable performances that lie ahead. This marks the beginning of your journey with DCOY, and we are thrilled to welcome you to our training grounds! 

Stay updated with DCOY’s future announcements through our official social media pages:

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/IASDanceCompany
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/iasdancetroupe_/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@feuiasdcoy

#IASFight
#StyledToMove

Caption by Ryona Claire Atienza
Pubmat by Angel Mae Contreras

message.text:
CONGRATULATIONS, AUDITIONEES! 🎉👏

After the successful auditions, we now proudly introduce our new batch of trainees! You’ve officially made it in the DCOY family!

You have showcased both talent and determination in braving the auditions. Once again, congratulations to all of you! We look forward to witnessing your growth and sharing the memorable performances that lie ahead. This marks the beginning of your journey with DCOY, and we are thrilled to welcome you to our training grounds! 

Stay updated with DCOY’s future announcements through our official social media pages:

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/IASDanceCompany
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/iasdancetroupe_/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@feuiasdcoy

#IASFight
#StyledToMove

Pubmat by Angel Mae Contreras

message.text:
CONGRATULATIONS, AUDITIONEES! 🎉👏

After the successful auditions, we now proudly introduce our new batch of trainees! You’ve officially made it in the DCOY family!

You have showcased both talent and determination in braving the auditions. Once again, congratulations to all of you! We look forward to witnessing your growth and sharing the memorable performances that lie ahead. This marks the beginning of your journey with DCOY, and we are thrilled to welcome you to our training grounds! 

Stay updated with DCOY’s future announcements through our official social media pages:
